					<description><![CDATA[<p>Augmodo Raises $21M to Scale Physical AI Inventory Technology Seattle-based Augmodo has raised $21 million in a new funding round to accelerate the growth of its wearable artificial intelligence platform</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/augmodo-raises-21m-expand-physical-ai/" data-wpel-link="internal">Augmodo Raises $21M to Expand Physical AI Platform Beyond Retail</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
