		<title>The New Playbook for Raising Capital in a Tough VC Market </title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/the-new-playbook-for-raising-capital-in-a-tough-vc-market/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Staff Reporter]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 15:30:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Venture Capital]]></category>
