<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you manage 150+ daily messages, you are the exact target market. It is for those who treat their inbox as a strict to-do list. The high entry fee is intentionally meant to filter out casual users. It is a highly specialized, elite platform.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Account Executives, Business Development Representatives, and Customer Success Managers will find the Read Statuses and Auto Follow-up sequences particularly lucrative for closing deals. Conversely, if you operate a business where email is a secondary communication channel, this software is entirely unnecessary. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Freelancers with tight budgets should prioritize spending their operational capital on essential software rather than luxury workflow enhancements.</span></p>
