<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you have the corporate budget, you can use it. You can hunt down a referral link or use the 7-day option. Experience it for yourself. See exactly how it lowers your daily stress levels.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Superhuman Email Review: FAQs</span></h2>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">How does Superhuman work?</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It works by replacing your default Gmail or Outlook web interface with a native, lightning-fast application. It caches your messages locally so they open instantly.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Is Superhuman worth it?</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For the right person, yes. If you are a founder, executive, real estate agent, or sales professional who spends more than two hours a day inside an inbox, the $30 a month is a bargain.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Is Superhuman free?</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">No, there is no permanent free tier, and there never has been. The company strictly positions itself as a premium, luxury software product. While you cannot use the software for free indefinitely, you can occasionally find a 7-day or 30-day trial if you are referred by a current active user. </span></p>
