<h2><b data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="22">Replit Review:</b> Pricing and Plans</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The trick to Replit pricing in 2026 is knowing what your usage credits are. The platform has shifted to a system in which you pay based on the power that you use.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Replit Free (Starter)</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ideal to start with. It includes general AI access and one public deployment. You also get free agent credits on a daily basis, free AI integration credits, and restricted agent intelligence.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Replit Core ($20/mo or $17/mo charged annually)</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The middle price. Comes with 20 dollars in monthly credits, Power Mode for the Agent, and unlimited personal projects. You are allowed to add five collaborators and export creations without the Replit badge.</span></p>
