<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Replit vs VS Code</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_199209" style="width: 1384px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-199209" class="wp-image-199209 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Replit-vs-VS-Code.jpg" alt="Replit vs VS Code" width="1374" height="770" /><p id="caption-attachment-199209" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Replit vs VS Code</p></div>
