<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In contrast, Replit is a browser‑based IDE that cuts out local setup entirely and focuses on instant access, collaboration, and built‑in hosting. VS Code wins when you want maximum customization, plugins, and offline‑first workflows</span></p>
