<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cursor IDE is another top Replit competitor. It is a local AI‑focused editor built on VS Code, optimized for LLM‑driven coding and refactoring. It&#8217;s ideal for professional developers who want deep AI integration but still prefer a local workflow and a full‑featured IDE. Replit&#8217;s advantage is that it runs entirely in the browser and offers instant deployment and hosting.</span></p>
