<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To summarize this <b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="40">Replit review</b>, the platform is an attractive choice to hobbyists, learners, indie makers, and small teams who are making lightweight apps or prototypes. With heavy-duty, production-grade systems, it can be better employed as a companion or prototyping platform than as an actual production platform.</span></p>
